ke the Unstable SMP and LifeSteal SMP</span></p><p></p><h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 64, 141);\">Modern AU</span></h3><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 178, 233);\">Modern AU (Alternate Universe) is a type of fan-created story or setting where characters from an existing work (like a game, movie, book, anime, or YouTube series) are reimagined in a normal world with normal settings without any supernatural creatures.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/er6Z2KbH33puydwSxkP8l.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 399px;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"http://C.ai\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 178, 233);\">C.ai</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 178, 233);\">: @</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://share.character.ai/70U7/683rfpna\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 178, 233);\">Birds_of_Paradise</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Im more active on there with more bots! Currently transferring them on here!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/IWFzhLYcsadGivZEGcj_x.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 400px;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 64, 141);\">ART CREDITS:</span></h3><p><code>@dizzy.png</code><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 178, 233);\">&nbsp;on TT</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 178, 233);\">or</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><code>@pea_404</code><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 178, 233);\">&nbsp;on Insta</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span 